---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Cost-Effective House Designs: Affordable and Efficient Living in Nepal";
const description = "Explore practical and budget-friendly house design ideas tailored for Nepali families. Discover techniques and materials that reduce costs while enhancing comfort and durability.";
const date = "2024-03-15";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="blog-post">
    <header>
      <p class="date">{new Date(date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
        year: 'numeric',
        month: 'long',
        day: 'numeric'
      })}</p>
      <h1>{title}</h1>
    </header>

    <img 
      src="https://www.karmod.eu/media/blog/270/prefab-container-homes-ghana_8.jpg"
      alt="Cost-Effective Nepali House Design"
      class="hero-image"
    />

    <div class="content">
      <p class="lead">Designing an affordable home in Nepal doesnâ€™t mean compromising on quality or style. With smart planning and efficient materials, Nepali homeowners can enjoy comfortable living at a reasonable price.</p>

      <h2>Budget-Friendly Building Materials</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Locally sourced stone and wood</li>
        <li>Eco-friendly bricks</li>
        <li>Recycled or upcycled materials</li>
        <li>Bamboo for roofing and interior decor</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Energy-Efficient Features</h2>
      <p>Incorporating energy-efficient elements helps reduce long-term costs:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Passive solar design to minimize heating costs</li>
        <li>Natural ventilation systems</li>
        <li>Low-energy lighting and appliances</li>
        <li>Water-saving fixtures</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Optimizing Small Spaces</h2>
      <p>For those on a budget, maximizing smaller spaces is crucial:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Open-plan layouts to make small rooms feel larger</li>
        <li>Multi-purpose furniture</li>
        <li>Ample storage solutions</li>
        <li>Natural light to enhance the sense of space</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
<style>
  .blog-post {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .date {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .content {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }
  img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  ul {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  a {
    color: #3498db;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
